This is a lightweight version of the DCDC TESTING procedere, with a focus on simple tests and ease of data retrieval.
All files are required for proper execution, but only MainTesting must be ran to begin testing.

Testing parameters can be configured at the top of MainTesting.

FetchBoardData will give you a list of all boards and their results on an Excel Sheet, and can also be used to retrieve
the scope trace data of any board. User must change destination paths or data will fail to download.

For now, all the tests that need be done are contained in Maintesting.